<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Sqlalchemy on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/sqlalchemy/</link><description>Recent content in Sqlalchemy on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/sqlalchemy/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SQLAlchemy error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/sqlalchemy-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/sqlalchemy-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Flask-SQLAlchemy encounters a problem executing a database query, such as connection failures, constraint violations, or SQL syntax errors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Database connection URI is misconfigured or unreachable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrity constraint violation (unique, foreign key, not null)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Query references a table or column that does not exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SQLAlchemy session is not properly committed or rolled back&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify the database URI:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URI&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;postgresql://user:pass@localhost/mydb&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SQLALCHEMY_TRACK_MODIFICATIONS&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;False&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle database errors in route handlers:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; sqlalchemy.exc &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; IntegrityError
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; flask_sqlalchemy &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; SQLAlchemy
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;db &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; SQLAlchemy(app)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@app.route&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/users&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, methods&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;POST&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;create_user&lt;/span&gt;():
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; user &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; User(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;request&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;form[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;name&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; db&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;session&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;add(user)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; db&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;session&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;commit()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;except&lt;/span&gt; IntegrityError:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; db&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;session&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;rollback()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;error&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;User already exists&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;}, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;409&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;id&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;id}, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;201&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;db.session.rollback()&lt;/code&gt; on any error:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; db&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;session&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;commit()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;except&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Exception&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; db&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;session&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;rollback()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;raise&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable query logging for debugging:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; logging
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;logging&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;getLogger(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;sqlalchemy.engine&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;setLevel(logging&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;INFO)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; User(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;db&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;session&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;add(user)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;db&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;session&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;commit()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# sqlalchemy.exc.IntegrityError: (psycopg2.errors.UniqueViolation)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# duplicate key value violates unique constraint &amp;#34;users_name_key&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/session-error/"&gt;Session error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>